scenario\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"Maher\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She posted about her BMI - and how little it reveals - in the mid-July TikTok.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3406, \"end\": 3409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.244511585124028e-62, \"text\": \"BMI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mid-July TikTok\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am 5 (feet) 10 (inches) and 200 pounds.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5 (feet\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"10 (inches\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"200 pounds\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I have about - and this is an estimate - but about 170 pounds of lean mass on me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an estimate\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"about 170 pounds\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"lean mass\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That BMI does not really tell you what I can do \\u2026 how fit I am.\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3611, \"end\": 3614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.244511585124028e-62, \"text\": \"BMI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a couple of numbers put together, does not tell you how much muscle I have or anything like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a couple\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"numbers\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"how much muscle\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articleYou should not want to look like an Olympian, experts say BMI measurements can overestimate body fat in athletes and people with a muscular build or a larger body frame.\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3831, \"end\": 3839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998658495, \"rank\": 6.923800846710207e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3854, \"end\": 3857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.244511585124028e-62, \"text\": \"BMI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Related articleYou\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"body fat\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3895}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3907}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"a muscular build\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"a larger body frame\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversely, BMI can underestimate body fat in older adults and anyone who has lost muscle, according to theHarvard T.H.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3978, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.244511585124028e-62, \"text\": \"BMI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Body_mass_index\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"body fat\", \"f